{"id":133858,"type":2,"name":"The Good Dinosaur","name_cn":"恐龙当家","date":"2015-11-25","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/8d/3b/133858_KvXAx.jpg","rating":{"rank":5528,"total":52,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":2,"4":5,"5":15,"6":20,"7":8,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.6},"summary":"　　继大获成功的《玩具总动员》系列、《海底总动员》、《飞屋环游记》、《机器人总动员》、《怪兽大学》等经典之作后，皮克斯动画工作室将于2014年推出第15部动画长片——《恐龙与男孩》(暂译)。影片目前正在紧锣密鼓的制作中，可供披露的素材很少，已经公布的消息仅仅是导演人选、北美上映日期与故事概念。 \r\n　　《恐龙与男孩》由皮克斯元老之一的鲍勃·彼德森执导，他曾担任《飞屋环游记》的联合导演，并为不少皮克斯动画献声。本次他除了身兼导演，也构思了影片的故事——如果6500万年前，小行星并没有撞击地球导致恐龙灭绝，那么世界会是什么样子？《恐龙与男孩》便从这个念头发散出去，讲述了一头雷龙与一个男孩的大冒险。 ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>恐龙当家</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>製作: </span><a href=\"/person/6816\">Walt Disney Pictures</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/7960\">Pixar Animation Studios</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>恐龙管家</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>恐龙与男孩</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>善良的恐龙</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>美好的恐龙世界</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>好恐龙</li><li><span>上映年度: </span>2015-11-25</li><li><span>片长: </span>100分钟</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>movies.disney.com/the-good-dinosaur</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>IMDb链接: </span>tt1979388</li><li><span>制片国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>导演: </span>Peter Sohn</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Enrico Casarosa / Bob Peterson</li><li><span>主演: </span>Raymond Ochoa / Jeffrey Wright / Steve Zahn / A.J. Buckley / Anna Paquin / Sam Elliott / Frances McDormand / Marcus Scribner</li><li><span>发行公司: </span>Walt Disney Studios Motion Pictures</li>","collection":{"on_hold":2,"dropped":9,"wish":13,"collect":83,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"pixar","count":23},{"name":"2015","count":20},{"name":"剧场版","count":16},{"name":"欧美","count":13},{"name":"动画电影","count":10},{"name":"皮克斯","count":7},{"name":"3D","count":5},{"name":"美国","count":4},{"name":"电影","count":3},{"name":"剧情","count":2},{"name":"2010s","count":1},{"name":"奇幻","count":1}